🔹 Step 11: Download Output (Optional)
👉 In build page → Artifacts
Download site/ folder

Open:

index.html
🔥 Common Errors (IMPORTANT)
❌ Jenkins not opening
✔ Run:

docker compose up -d
❌ Port already used
✔ Change in docker-compose:

- "9090:8080"
❌ Pipeline fails (script error)
✔ Use exact script above (indentation matters)

❌ HTML not showing
✔ Ensure plugin installed:
HTML Publisher Plugin

